Unravel a magical detective story!
To save your father from a strange sickness, you have to dive deep into an intricate crime case revolving around the kidnapping of a mysterious Beauty married to Puss in Boots. And this is only the beginning... Explore a magical city full of fairytale characters and their secrets and solve this fantastic Hidden Object mystery!
Immerse yourself in a world of intrigue and secrets in this dark and gloomy town full of magical inhabitants. An unforgettable Hidden Object Thriller awaits you!

============================================
